=== DEPRESSURIZATION ===
# id: 36
# title: The Depressurization Event
# chinese_title: 减压事件
# category: Hazard
# mode: dungeon

A groaning sound echoes through the bulkhead as micro-fractures spider across the viewport. The pressure differential is building — you have seconds before the glass fails and the section vents to space. Emergency bulkheads are visible at both ends of the corridor.

* [Race to seal the emergency bulkhead]
  ~ gain_radical("风")
  "风" (fēng) — wind, air current
* [Use an emergency patch from your kit]
  ~ gain_xp(20)
  "补" (bǔ) — to repair, to patch
* [Brace for the depressurization]
  ~ damage(8)
  "压" (yā) — pressure
